
& gunnery-spotting
 
 >> Help: Gunnery-Spotting (Gunnery Skill)
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Used when providing spotting data to someone firing artillery
 (see 'help spot').
 
 To see specifics on spotting weapons, type 'help spot-weapons'.
 
 For a detailed look at this skill, see our online documentation:
 docs.btmux.com/index.php/Skills%2C_Stats%2C_Attributes%2C_and_Advantages
 
